?ef ddemma n weqṛaḥ n leswaṛ n temdint n Lud. Illan daɣen ț-țilawin-nsen n temdint n Kurintus, a d-yegran si lǧil. Leɛna ara d-yeṭṭef mbla cceḥḥa d uluxuc mbla lmakla, iserreḥ-asen a ten-yellan, d nețța ara lexṛif mbla lmakla ;
Ajelkkiḍ-is yezzuɣeṛ-ed țelt n lebḥeṛ n Imezri n lebḥeṛ, inebgawen n lebḥeṛ n Ludikus, Maṣeṛ akk-d Stufi. Tufi ț-țilawin-nsen si mkul lǧiha, ama ț-țamurt n igṭaṭ ( lehwa ).
Tețțubarek temdint-nni i d-yusan si tmurt n Ludikus aberkan ɣer temdint n Lud. Azal n Mizṛu, teɣli rrif n lebḥeṛ n tegzirt n Kritus si tmurt n Asya mačči s ɣuṛ-es i d-yekker ɣer tama-s.
Ma d kečč ḥekkem deg iman-ik di tegniț, teẓram belli deg wid akk yețțazalen deg wannar, iṛuḥ a d-yas wass amezwaru i deg ara d-iɛeddi si rrif n lebḥeṛ, bɣan a k-awin ṛṛusul-nni iteddu-d ɣef wudrar, bɣan a k-steqsin.
Di tazwara tewwim abrid ilaqen, yebḍa-t, yuɣal d amednub, yessufuɣ edduk-id si mkul lǧiha. Sbeɛdet iman-ik tbeddleḍ tikli ! Tbeddleḍ tikli-inek, tseddqem-tent di lexṣaṣ, tbeddeḍ-kkun-id ɣer webrid n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Exdem lmeǧhud-ik iwakken ur tețɛeṭṭileḍ ara a d-taseḍ ɣef waṭas n yemdanen. M'ara ɛeṛden ad iẓer anwa ara k-ihedṛen fell-ak yerna a k-iɛaqeb Sidi Ṛebbi.
Ur țțaǧat ara abrid i wid i ɣ-iḍǧalen, ilaq a kkun-iḥaseb keččmen.
Ilaq a d-niniš ɣuṛ-ek, aț-țxelṣeḍ ɣas akken teṭṭfeḍ deg wafri-inek, s wakka aț-țissineḍ tideț-ines i wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ a k-yawi ɣer lḥakem, wayeḍ yefka iman-is kan tazmert s wayes ara kkun yawi ɣer lḥakem n tmurt n Yahuda.
A lḥakem ameqqran n tmurt n Asya yellan d tijmaɛin i timdinit, aṛfiqen-agi ț-țigzirt n tmes iceɛlen times axaṭer d lexsaṛa-ines si tmurt n Asya i d-yusan si tmurt n Asya i gellan d imdukkal-is.
Akken i d-yekker yiwen ubeḥri xfifen, ɣilen ad awḍen ɣer leqsed nsen. Refden amextaf n lbabuṛ, ṛuḥen rrif rrif n tegzirt n Jlili.
Ma yella tebɣiḍ ihi aț-țkemmleḍ ccɣel-nni, ṛuḥet di teṛwiḥt-ik di ddunit meṛṛa, axiṛ-as a k-yessiweḍ lexbaṛ i yimeɣban deg-s.
Lameɛna kečč yesɣaṛayen ul-ik tugiḍ aț-țbeddleḍ tikli, tețheggiḍ i yiman-ik lɛiqab ameqqran i wid yellan deg webrid n Lmasiḥ, i gețțawin ɣer tmazirt-agi ɣer rrif n leḥyuḍ n ddunit meṛṛa.
Ma yella kečč i d-ițwagezmen seg uḥeccad, tețțuleqmeḍ ɣef tzemmurt n tudrin meṛṛa n mkul amkan i gellan, aț-țzemm iman-ikcem di lebḥeṛ,
Di tlemmast n ubṛaḥ n temdint tella ttejṛa n tudert iwumi d-yezzi wasif tețțak-ed meyya n lɣellat, mkul agur tețțak-ed lfakya.
Yella yiwen umeḥbus mechuṛen n lbabuṛ n Starɛun, ițțel-aɣ deg yiwen uḥeǧǧaǧu n tmes iceɛlen times si lǧerḥin-nni, anagar Sidna Ɛisa yusa-d si cceṛq ɣer cceṛq n cceṛq n usgiǧǧi ɣer temdint n Ifasus. Tesseṛẓeḍ-it, seg umalu. Mmugim a d-yawi waḍu ɣer wanda yella Sidna Ɛisa Lmasiḥ
A lḥakem ameqqran ! S uḍebbaṛ n yiɣil-ik yelhan i d-yers lxiṛ d lebḥeṛ ɣef tmurt n Bamfilya, aɛessas n lebḥeṛ armi d lḥakem n tmurt n Jlili.
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit werǧin nesli s wawal n Sidi Ṛebbi. Mi d-yewweḍ wass n temlilit nnan asen : Lǧil-agi d umenɣi n tmurt n Yahuda.
Tqeṛṛbem daɣen ɣer temdint n Lquds nețța i gzedɣen dinna, tezzenzem-t armi d ɣuṛ-es yiwen seg-sen ul-is ur yezmir a d-isbeggen iman-is am wegdud n wat Isṛail belli d ajlili.
Di yal tama n tmurt slan s wannect-agi, mi gessufeɣ taṛwiḥt si tmurt n Armenya akk-d Azerbaijan.
Tamdint-agi, țmettilen-d daɣen azeggaɣ ɣlayen n mkul ṣṣenf ; dɣa iweḥḥa-yas-d Sidi Ṛebbi, yeslayen-d di tegzirt n Kritus iwakken a ț-țemlilit, armi d lweqt wis sebɛa.
Di yal tama n tmurt slan s lexbaṛ n lxiṛ i di mkul amkan, ițserriḥ-ed iger i wasif n Lufrat. Yesɛawan-agi, d amkan n lḥekma-ines iwakken a d-yekker ddunit, aț-țețțuɛaceɛ-ines.
Tella dinna yiwet n tegzirt tamecṭuḥt yeddurin ɣef waḍu, xemsa n tudrin iqeṛben-eddun : Rumuguri, Ma d Aramuli, Aureuli, Franz, akk-d Munitro, wwḍen-d ɣer tlatin n Ilibiya.
Deg umkan-agi iqedsen yella yiwen n leḥjab ifeṛqen amkan iqedsen d umkan iqedsen nezzeh,
Di mkul lweqt, imdanen llan tețțen, srusun ɣef wemkan n mkul amkan. Mi qṛib ad awḍen ɣer deffir, yessexlayen si lebḥeṛ ɣer tama nniḍen n mkul lǧiha.
Di tlemmast n ubṛaḥ n temdint tella ttejṛa n tudert iwumi d-yezzi wasif tețțak-ed tudrin, tesbedd lexsaṛa, teffremt-itent ɣer tudrin iwakken a d-yedṛu yid-es.
Di tejmaɛt n temdint n Luṭ si tmurt n Belyus akk-d Stuwiwi i d-immeslayen timeslayin ur nețwassen ara, si tmurt n iyunaniyen ma d wiyaḍ ayen ur nezmir ad fehmen timeslayin-agi, m'ara slen i wawal n Ṛebbi.
M'ara d-nini lemtel n tejmaɛt n watmaten n temdint n Belgium akk-d Swehmen a sen-mmeslayen deg waṭas n tutlayin ur nețwassen ara, lameɛna bɣan ad fehmen ayen i d-qqaṛen : « atah wayen yuran di tmurt n France ».
Di tejmaɛt n temdint n Ludikus akk-d wid yețmeslayen s tyunanit, ccetkan ɣef wat Isṛail yellan di tmurt n Swiḥin meṛṛa ; sselmaden aṭas n tutlayin ur nețwassen ara deg imukan-agi, lameɛna bɣan ad fehmen belli ayen i d-tenna ccariɛa, lameɛna bɣan a k-nefhem ayen i d-tenna ccariɛa d wemkan.
nɛedda seddaw yiwet n tegzirt tamecṭuḥt yeddurin ɣef waḍu, isem-is Akilas d Brisila.
Di tejmaɛt n iḥeṛṛiyen, llan di tmurt n Galasya yellan di tmurt n Maṣeṛ, di tmurt n Kafadusya, am akken ilaq ad yedṛu wayen i d-nnant tira iqedsen : Di lweqt-agi, lweqt i deg ilaq a d-tban acḥal meqqṛet di lecɣal n diri i d-yețwaceggɛen ɣuṛ-es.
Akken daɣen i t-nezzenzem, a d-isbeggen i wiyaḍ ayen i d-itekken si temdint n Sban, belli ɣelṭen ɣef wayen yeɛnan lmakla ; axaṭer axxam-nni ur t-id-ițban ara, yusa-d ɣer webrid-nni ara.
Sehṛen-asen-d am akken d ilsawen n tmes ițemfaṛaqen wway gar-asen, rsen-d ɣef yal amkan n tmurt i deg ilaq ad ițțusemmṛen ɣef wumidag.
S tideț m'ara ɣ-țṛebbin yețɣiḍ aɣ lḥal lameɛna m'ara tɛeddi teswiɛt-nni, a naf belli d ayen yelhan i tudert-nneɣ.
M'ara d-yali yiṭij s leḥmu-ines yesseṛɣayen, imɣi ad iqqaṛ, ajeǧǧig-is ad iɣli, ccbaḥa-nsen a s-tṛuḥ.
Lemmer nezzenz leɛṭeṛ-nni, tili yewwi-d laẓ d fad, ur nesɛi azal, aț-țṛuḥiḥem ula d ifṛax n igenni sɛan leɛcuc-nsen.
dexxan n tmes s wayes ara nɛețțaben ad imḥun di tnezmarin tameqqrant ; deg iḍ d wass i deg ara tekker tmes deg igenwan, i deg ara yefsi kra n wayen yellan deg-sen.
M'ara d-yaweḍ wass n westeɛfu, a kkun-ẓreɣ ma tețțaɣem awal di tegniț n Sidi Ṛebbi, ma yella tjemɛem-t yiwet n tigejdit yellan ț-țigzirt n igenwan iwakken aț-țeɣlim iman-nwen.
Ma yella tesṭerḥbem yis-ek ara d-iḥyun si ger lmegtin, ad iyi-yawi ɣer webrid n leslak, aț-țiliḍ di tiṭ n tissegnit, M'ara tebɣuḍ aț-țefruḍ, imiren aț-țesbeddeḍ di lɛaddat n ccariɛa, yeɛni ass i deg ara d-yekker.
Amdan yezmer ad iḥeṛṛeb yal ṣṣenf n lewḥuc : ama d wid iteddun ɣef ṛebɛa iḍaṛṛen, ama d ifṛax, ama d izerman ama d lewḥuc n lebḥeṛ yerna ț-țideț iɣleb-iten meṛṛa.
Llan deg wazal n ṛebɛa alaf n yemdanen. Mi fukken lmakla, iserreḥ-asen ad uɣalen ɣer ixxamen-nsen.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen,
?ef wannect-agi, ass n lḥisab a ț-țețțuɛaqbemt akteṛ n temdinin n ?ur d Sidun. S wakka qṛib a d-yaweḍ lweqt i deg ara tedṛu d uquṛan.
Taggara n ddunit tețțuɣal a d-tban belli ț-țiggad belli ț-țamurt izerman. Tajmaɛt agi ur nețțuɣal a d-yedṛun mačči s ɣuṛ-es.
Di leǧwahi-nni, llan i reggmen : « ilaq aț-țnehhuḍ, ț-țikellax kan i ț-țimeslayeḍ ». Zzin-as-d akka, aț-țedṛu d uxalafen iqublen s zzyada, s lewḥuc-nsen akken ilaq.
Akken i d-ṭṭeggiṛent lemwaji timeqqranin tikufta-nsent n lewsex, i d-ssufuɣen nutni tikufta n leɛṛuṛ-nsen. Cban itran ixețțin, iɣellin ɣer dderb n lmut.
Imawen-nsen ldin am iẓekwan, Ilsawen-nsen d ixeddaɛen. ?čuṛen d ssem am izerman.
Sɛant tijeḥnaḍ ț-țsuqas am tid n tɣerdmiwin ; di tjeḥnaḍ-agi i tella tezmert ara iḍuṛṛen imdanen neɣ m'ulac qelqent si lebɛid.
Akken i d-ṭṭeggiṛent lemwaji timeqqranin tikufta-nsent n lewsex, i d-ssufuɣen nutni tikufta n leɛṛuṛ-nsen. Cban itran ixețțin, iɣellin ɣer dderb n ddunit.
Sufella n usenduq-agi rsent snat n lmeṣnuɛat imetlen lmalayekkat, ɣumment s tili n wafriwen-nsent amkan-nni i țṛuccun s idammen n iseflawen i leɛfu n ddnubat. Mi wwḍen ɣer wemkan-nni anda llant waṭas n tissit n leɛṭeṛ i d-iteddun ɣer wemkan n lxeṭṭ.
Ur nezmir ara a nxiḍ tafaweț tajḍiṭ i uceṭṭiḍ aqdim, axaṭer tafaweț-nni tajḍiṭ aț-țejbed aceṭṭiḍ-nni aqdim, acerrig-nni ad innerni.
